{"tid":2398167,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民放白花哀自由湮滅","createTime":"2021-02-07T05:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T05:15:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a31e35b76033aa5e1daabfbc755938ae6e8acf81","tid":2398167,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210207/IR4AB54JHJHV5F5Q7CUY4OOO74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210207%2FIR4AB54JHJHV5F5Q7CUY4OOO74%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOfZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=47d0de25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210207%2FIR4AB54JHJHV5F5Q7CUY4OOO74%2F&h=cfead0e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210207/IR4AB54JHJHV5F5Q7CUY4OOO74/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民放白花哀自由湮滅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oLt2HOAbId0Lo1-4WbVOftUlcBk=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NHFZFICJHJDKVDKJ3RJ65K546A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoLt2HOAbId0Lo1-4WbVOftUlcBk%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNHFZFICJHJDKVDKJ3RJ65K546A.jpg&h=80f46645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李卓人（右）及蔡耀昌在鐵馬掛上「平反六四 公義必勝」橫額抗議政權打壓。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】食環署人員昨用鐵馬圍封支聯會的維園年宵攤位，但封殺的不單止是一個年宵攤位，而是同時毀滅爭取民主自由、討回公道的聲音。支持支聯會多年的市民批評極權政府倒行逆施，令碩果僅存的自由空間消失，痛心不已。有市民在食環署的冰冷鐵馬外擺放兩束白花，哀香港自由湮滅。年宵場上，大開殺戒，令迎向新春的日子，添上沉痛和欷歔。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政權打壓 年宵花檔也容不下  支聯會變陣 市民捐款抗極權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2QBsidZeus9PD8SrkH42MpQ4cKQ=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZFX2MQXNBVFCHKG57QCKUWKOTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2QBsidZeus9PD8SrkH42MpQ4cKQ%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZFX2MQXNBVFCHKG57QCKUWKOTY.jpg&h=baac10e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■支聯會攤位被封殺，有市民放下兩束白花哀自由已死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睹拆「共命運」橫額哽咽<br />\n<br />\n不願上鏡的七旬婦向本報表示，她多年來一直支持民主以及支聯會發展，當目睹支聯會主席李卓人在維園收拾花束，清拆「自由」、「共命運」橫額，感到十分痛心，一時之間難以接受香港竟淪落至此。她哽咽地說，香港碩果僅存的自由空間越來越少，「唔啱（政府）聽嘅說話，（政府）一定唔可以畀你公開（宣揚）」。年長的她表示不會離港，但其兒子有意奔向自由的台灣。<br />\n<br />\n自稱立場屬民主派的蔡太多年來都會到支聯會的攤檔購買小飾物以示支持，惟食環署人員將支聯會年宵攤檔趕離場，她慨嘆「心情好灰，同幾年前行花市嘅心情唔同晒」，批評港府用盡方法箝制港人思想。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EJlVpbJ6V3no2Iacdht-PDUC4X4=/501x639/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5Z6BKQG3GJCQNPN5XI23PAX2D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEJlVpbJ6V3no2Iacdht-PDUC4X4%3D%2F501x639%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5Z6BKQG3GJCQNPN5XI23PAX2D4.jpg&h=97a181e6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}